                    <summary type="html">
                        &lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;we showcased the twitter feed with @peppertw, &lt;a href=&quot;http://peppertweet.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://peppertweet.com/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&#039;s a pet project written by me and other developers/designers in Italy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The project isn&#039;t open sourced yet, we have still have work to do, but if you need it we can provide you an hosted installation for your event. &lt;/p&gt;
