                                            <content type="html">
                            &lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;we showcased the twitter feed with @peppertw, &lt;a href=&quot;http://peppertweet.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://peppertweet.com/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It&#039;s a pet project written by me and other developers/designers in Italy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The project isn&#039;t open sourced yet, we have still have work to do, but if you need it we can provide you an hosted installation for your event. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The plus is that it streams and shows also photos inside a tweet and you can collect them for future use.&lt;br/&gt;We use it for collecting Global Code Retreat photos (soon available)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You can see an example of the latest event we supported: &lt;a href=&quot;http://uan12.peppertweet.com&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://uan12.peppertweet.com&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://uan12.peppertweet.com/single&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;http://uan12.peppertweet.com/single&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hope it helps :P&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;cirpo&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;                        </content>
                    
